rComments: Prof. Slade was awesome. He talks a lot though, so his lectures can sometimes seem a bit dreadful. Especially when he goes on tangents... That being said, hes very knowledgeable and is always there to help students. The material needs to be thought about critically though, and you need to go above and beyond to do well but its definitely do-able!

Great prof - knew the material and made it understandable, even though a lot of it came from the readings. Extremely approachable, and he also has a great sense of humour! Would definitely take another class with him.

He is a great professor, very helpful and knows the topics. He is approachable, very nice and tries to engage in class discussion. The TA's were less helpful. He always responds right away. Take his classes
